# I think right now that Mini has to have at least three atoms per residue,
# hence the virtual atoms.
NAME CU
IO_STRING  CU X
TYPE LIGAND
PROPERTIES METAL
AA UNK
ATOM CU   Cu2p  Cu2p 2.00
ATOM  V1  VIRT  VIRT 0.00
ATOM  V2  VIRT  VIRT 0.00
ATOM  V3  VIRT  VIRT 0.00
ATOM  V4  VIRT  VIRT 0.00
BOND CU    V1
BOND CU    V2
BOND CU    V3
BOND CU    V4
NBR_ATOM CU
NBR_RADIUS 5.0
# tetrahedral geometry with 2.2 distance from center to vertex
# chirality is defined so that viewing from V1 to CU, V2-V3-V4 are in clockwise direction.
ICOOR_INTERNAL   CU      0.000000    0.000000    0.000000  CU     V1    V2
ICOOR_INTERNAL    V1     0.000000    0.000000    2.200000  CU     V1    V2
ICOOR_INTERNAL    V2     0.000000   70.500000    2.200000  CU     V1    V2
ICOOR_INTERNAL    V3   120.000000   70.500000    2.200000  CU     V1    V2
ICOOR_INTERNAL    V4  -120.000000   70.500000    2.200000  CU     V1    V2
